    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit maintains its mechanical integrity with a recently overhauled Double-VANOS system and documented rear subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for the longitudinal rigidity of this platform. Power is routed through a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to an M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring linear power delivery and exceptional corner-exit traction. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, while the individual throttle bodies provide the signature induction note and sharp throttle response enthusiasts demand. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains robust and track-capable.",
      "price": 34500.0,
