      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants a great car without the brand-new price tag. It runs smoothly and is totally ready for your next road trip! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home!",
